text: Cheng Chu Sian (born 1 March 1986) is an archer from Malaysia. Chu Sian competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Cheng Chu SianChu Sian CHENG == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian archers Category:Olympians for Malaysia
